CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 10, 1958, pg. 14, reads: "Fellowship Principals - Among those who shared responsibility for the success of the Council of Churchwomen's May Fellowship Day at East Liberty Presbyterian Church, May 2, were... Bottom row, clockwise: Mmes. LeRoy Ellenburger, George H. Haden, chairman; Marguerite Hofer, group leader; Merle D. Chamberlain, president, and Willa Mae Rice, vice president. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of women, including Mrs. LeRoy Ellenburger, Mrs. George H. Haden, Marguerite Hofer, Merle D. Chamberlain, and Willa Mae Rice seated on right, posed in East Liberty Presbyterian Church
